{"tid":2080118,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【經濟客飯】派錢一萬的經濟分析 - 曾國平","createTime":"2020-06-26T08:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T08:12:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2139e98a4acaf22079e436cb18f843a3e93c47fd","tid":2080118,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200626/MJTHG5VTNKPFTXDDE4BTONYMUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200626%2FMJTHG5VTNKPFTXDDE4BTONYMUY%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=911a7809\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200626%2FMJTHG5VTNKPFTXDDE4BTONYMUY%2F&h=6ee5effc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200626/MJTHG5VTNKPFTXDDE4BTONYMUY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【經濟客飯】派錢一萬的經濟分析 - 曾國平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LqftHE6Fa6NcLaYpxTQXw566ATY=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I3KPWCUVOZW2K3EOIXYBWGRTUU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLqftHE6Fa6NcLaYpxTQXw566ATY%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI3KPWCUVOZW2K3EOIXYBWGRTUU.jpg&h=e413c56e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n派錢除了應付經濟不景，更重要是將花錢的權力交回市民手中，市民要如何使用，不用學者說三道四。 資料圖片&lt;br /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n派錢1萬可以申請，某大網媒為此訪問經濟學者，學者估計市民大約會花一至兩成，又舉例指若市民本身已打算買新電話<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n學者的答案既斷估，也<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n其實只是將1萬元儲起來而已。這兩類消費者佔多少，學者再神通廣大也難以估計。<br />\n<br />\n錯重點，錯在擔心市民到底會消費幾多。與其這樣擔心，不如取消派錢，由政府花錢去搞大白象工程好了，那就肯定全數花光，「乘數效應」強勁，有助GDP。其實，派錢除了應付經濟不景，同樣重要（或更重要）的功能是將花錢的權力交回市民手中，減少政府浪費。市民要如何使用，不用學者說三道四。<br />\n<br />\n曾國平<br />\n美國維珍尼亞理工大學經濟系副教授<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/economics3.0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Feconomics3.0%2F&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h%2Fch229KM6nXCMtlUoiobV8%3D&h=92749740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/economics3.0/</a><br />\n本欄逢周五刊出"}]}